# Environment Configuration Example
# Copy this file to .env or .env.local for local environment variables
# DO NOT commit actual API keys or secrets to git!

# Optional client-side default provider configs (if applicable)
# VITE_DEFAULT_LLM_PROVIDER=groq
# VITE_DEFAULT_LLM_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# Note: Resume Intelligence operates as a Bring Your Own Key (BYOK) client-side application.
